ðŸ“ƒ My Story
Hello, I am Jakub Patrik. My deep interests are programming and business, a perfect balance of both. I've dived into computer science only a couple of years ago, yet I consider myself an independent and curiosity-driven student with a rapid learning curve.

ðŸ§ Coding Skills
I've been proudly creating websites, both raw HTML, CSS, JS, and WordPress. Further, I discovered Java and Python, where I landed my logical programming foundations. However, to take it one more step ahead I shifted my focus towards programming apps in Flutter-cross platform programming toolkit developed by Google.

ðŸ’ªBusiness Skills
I've started my marketing journey with an internship as an Online Marketing Intern, where I've successfully helped promote standup events all over Slovakia. Next, I've been expanding my knowledge with numerous Google Analytics or Ads Search courses. 

MottoðŸ˜Ž
"When one wants to build something, he must be able to sell it."
